Package: wickra.exchange
Type: Package
Title: Streaming-Native Crypto Exchange Connectivity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-exchange over its C ABI hub: one synchronous,
    pull-based API over the ten largest crypto exchanges, plus offline paper and
    replay simulators that share the exact same API. The same strategy runs
    paper, replay and live by swapping the constructor.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-exchange
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-exchange/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-exchange C ABI shared library (WKEX_LIB) and its
    header (WKEX_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
